author: rhuijben
msg: Apply a few tweaks of the repos-repos diff to the repos-wc diff.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/diff_editor.c
(dir_baton,
file_baton): Add has_propchange boolean.
(make_dir_baton,
make_file_baton): Use a default of 8 changes, as we will at least
receive the entry props for every node touched.
(apply_propchanges): Remove local reimplementation of svn_prop__patch().
(file_diff): Fetch original_repos_relpath for the node, not for the op-root.
(close_directory,
close_file): Use has propchange to decide whether to report property
changes. Use svn_prop__patch.
(change_file_prop,
change_dir_prop): Filter dav props. Set has_propchange.
